[Remember it is summer in the southern hemisphere, which means that it is now their anthrax season. Livestock anthrax is sporadic in Namibia but a constant concern in their national parks. - Mod.MHJ

HealthMap/ProMED-mail map of Namibia: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=6142934,163.]
